'''法拉第未来'''（{{lang-en|'''Faraday Future'''}}），是一家總部位於美國的智慧电动汽车公司。法拉第未来成立于2014年，总部位于加州[[加迪纳_(加利福尼亚州)|加迪纳]]；至2016年1月，该公司员工增长至1000余人<ref name="forbes-2016-01-05">{{cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/aarontilley/2016/01/05/faraday-future-were-going-to-move-a-lot-faster-than-tesla/ |title=Faraday Future: We're Going To Move A Lot Faster Than Tesla |first=Aaron |last=Tilley |work=Forbes |date=2016-01-05 |accessdate=2016-01-07 |archive-date=2016-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107204430/http://www.forbes.com/sites/aarontilley/2016/01/05/faraday-future-were-going-to-move-a-lot-faster-than-tesla/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。公司的投资合作伙伴是[[贾跃亭|贾跃亭]]领导的[[乐视集团|乐视集团]]（{{lang-en|LeEco}}）。

法拉第未来命名自电机技术基本原则之一的[[法拉第感应定律|法拉第感应定律]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.shearcomfort.com/blog/faraday-future-exclusive-interview/|title=Faraday Future Talks AI, Multi-Seat EVs in Exclusive Interview|date=2016-06-03|website=Shear Comfort Auto Blog|language=en-US|access-date=2016-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108111057/http://www.shearcomfort.com/blog/faraday-future-exclusive-interview/|archive-date=2017-01-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，后者纪念英国科学家[[迈克尔·法拉第|迈克尔·法拉第]]发现了电磁感应。2016年1月，在美国公司消费电子展上，法拉第未来首次推出概念车单座FFZERO1<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wired.com/2016/01/forget-faraday-futures-crazy-concept-car-it-has-bigger-plans/|title=Forget Faraday Future’s Crazy Concept Car. It Has Bigger Plans|website=WIRED|language=en-US|access-date=2016-06-08|archive-date=2016-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230123718/https://www.wired.com/2016/01/forget-faraday-futures-crazy-concept-car-it-has-bigger-plans/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年1月3日，消费电子展中法拉第未来推出量产车FF91及生产计划。2021年7月22日，法拉第未來透過與[[特殊目的收購公司|特殊目的收購公司]]Property Solutions Acquisition合併，在[[納斯達克|納斯達克]]掛牌上市。<ref>{{cite news |title=法拉第未來收市僅升1.4%　賈躍亭：必須回國 |url=https://inews.hket.com/article/3012908/%E3%80%90%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E3%80%91%E6%B3%95%E6%8B%89%E7%AC%AC%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%94%B6%E5%B8%82%E5%83%85%E5%8D%871.4-%E3%80%80%E8%B3%88%E8%BA%8D%E4%BA%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E5%9B%9E%E5%9C%8B%EF%BC%88%E9%99%84%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%EF%BC%89 |work=[[香港經濟日報|香港經濟日報]] |date=2021-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210723040058/https://inews.hket.com/article/3012908/%E3%80%90%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E3%80%91%E6%B3%95%E6%8B%89%E7%AC%AC%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%94%B6%E5%B8%82%E5%83%85%E5%8D%871.4-%E3%80%80%E8%B3%88%E8%BA%8D%E4%BA%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E5%9B%9E%E5%9C%8B%EF%BC%88%E9%99%84%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%EF%BC%89 |archivedate=2021-07-23}}</ref>

== 厂址 ==
2015年11月，法拉第未来宣布为第一个制造工厂投资10亿美元。美国[[加州|加州]]、[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]]、[[路易斯安纳州|路易斯安纳州]]和[[内华达州|内华达州]]都作为候选的工厂地址<ref>{{Cite news |title=A Mysterious Electric Carmaker has its Sights on Tesla |url=http://fortune.com/2015/11/05/faraday-future-tesla-mystery-electric-car/ |first=Don |last=Reisinger |work=Fortune |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2015-12-10 |archive-date=2015-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124200143/http://fortune.com/2015/11/05/faraday-future-tesla-mystery-electric-car/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年12月，法拉第未来选址内华达州北拉斯维加斯市<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/faraday-future-picks-nevada-site-for-1-billion-electric-car-investment-1449710099 |title=Faraday Future Picks Nevada Site for $1 Billion Electric-Car Investment |first=Mike |last=Ramsey |work=The Wall Street Journal |date=2015-12-09 |accessdate=2016-01-07 |archive-date=2016-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106101853/http://www.wsj.com/articles/faraday-future-picks-nevada-site-for-1-billion-electric-car-investment-1449710099 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并支付5亿美元给[[AECOM|AECOM]]进行基础建造<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.constructiondive.com/news/aecom-snags-500m-contract-to-build-nv-faraday-future-plant/428476/|title=AECOM snags $500M contract to build NV Faraday Future plant|date=2016-10-16|work=Construction Dive|accessdate=2016-12-19|archive-date=2016-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110100611/http://www.constructiondive.com/news/aecom-snags-500m-contract-to-build-nv-faraday-future-plant/428476/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年4月，工程建造开始，内华达州的额外所需的基础设施已经正式获得州议会同意，但后续审批仍处搁置状态，以等待验证法拉第的未来财务状况良好，并完全能够筹集到足够的资金为整个项目提供资金<ref name="WSJ41316">{{cite news |url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/electric-car-maker-faraday-breaks-ground-in-nevada-1460589107 |title=Electric Car Maker Faraday Breaks Ground in Nevada Startup aided by promise of state incentives moving ahead on first vehicle |first=Mike |last=Ramsey |work=The Wall Street Journal |date=2016-04-13 |accessdate=2016-04-15 |archive-date=2016-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414172928/http://www.wsj.com/articles/electric-car-maker-faraday-breaks-ground-in-nevada-1460589107 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。至2018年，该工程将获得2.15亿美元的{{le|税收激励|tax holiday}}，以及{{convert|4|mile|km|adj=on|0|abbr=out}}的铁路专用线；新工厂面积将有3亿平方英尺(2800万平方米)、全职员工达到4500人<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.northlasvegastribune.com/north-las-vegas-car-plan-begins-construction/ |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20161211221718/http://www.northlasvegastribune.com/north-las-vegas-car-plan-begins-construction/ |title= Faraday Future Approved for Apex Rail Spur |date= 2016-08-30 |archivedate= 2016-12-11 |work= North Las Vegas Tribune |accessdate= 2016-12-11 |deadurl= yes }}</ref>。

2016年5月24日，加州[[瓦列霍_(加利福尼亚州)|瓦列霍]]宣布在2016年5月31日举行市议会特别会议，投票进行独家谈判协议。这代表加州正式邀请法拉第未来进入到{{le|马雷岛|Mare Island}}；这也被视为近几年来，继{{le|菲斯克汽车公司|Fisker Automotive}}在[[莫雷诺谷|莫雷诺谷]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/business/autos/la-fi-hy-karma-car-factory-20160617-snap-story.html |title=Karma comes around again: California's newest car factory aims to rival Tesla |date=2016-06-17 |accessdate=2016-06-17 |archive-date=2016-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617150042/http://www.latimes.com/business/autos/la-fi-hy-karma-car-factory-20160617-snap-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>建厂后，第二家创新汽车制造商将在加州设立制造工厂。它可以为当地经济带来了数亿美元的新投资<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cityofvallejo.net/common/pages/DisplayFile.aspx?itemId=3962563 |title=City of Vallejo schedules May 31 vote on Agreement with Faraday Future for exclusive negotiations on 153 Acers |date=2016-05-24 |accessdate=2016-05-24 |archive-date=2016-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160528085826/http://www.cityofvallejo.net/common/pages/DisplayFile.aspx?itemId=3962563 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年5月31日，市议会一致同意进行六个月的独家谈判协议<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-faraday-vallejo-20160531-snap-story.html|title=Tesla rival Faraday gets one step closer to building electric cars in Vallejo|last=Times|first=Los Angeles|website=latimes.com|access-date=2016-06-06|archive-date=2016-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605182206/http://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-faraday-vallejo-20160531-snap-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.emvalley.com/news/weekly-electromobility-news-5/|title=Weekly Electromobility News – Electromobility News|website=www.emvalley.com|access-date=2016-06-06|archive-date=2016-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810064029/http://www.emvalley.com/news/weekly-electromobility-news-5/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 产品 ==
2015年6月，《{{le|汽車潮流 (雜誌)|Motor Trend|汽车潮流}}》杂志刊登的一篇文章，介绍了一些未来法拉第未来电动汽车的参数：在特定能源值上，它将比特斯拉S高出15%的性能。它利用多电池解决方案，解决单个电池和组织电池的可更换机制，并将改进大规模生产中的模块化设计方法<ref>{{Cite news |title=New Electric Car Company Emerges: Faraday Future |url=http://www.motortrend.com/news/new-california-based-electric-car-company-emerges-faraday-future/ |first=Kelly |last=Pleskot |work=Motor Trend |date=2015-11-06 |accessdate=2015-12-10 |archive-date=2015-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210214727/http://www.motortrend.com/news/new-california-based-electric-car-company-emerges-faraday-future/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年11月的{{le|LA汽车展|LA Auto Show}}上，设计主管理查德·金（{{lang|en|Richard Kim}}）讨论了他将设计一款汽车，包括内部网络进入、车载娱乐、人体工学设计等<ref>{{Cite news |title=Faraday Future’s 2017 Tesla Model S rival with a 300+ mile range will charge into CES 2016 |url=http://finance.yahoo.com/news/faraday-future-2017-tesla-model-195120592.html |first=Miles |last=Branman |work=Yahoo Finance |date=2015-11-30 |accessdate=2015-12-10 |archive-date=2015-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210021802/http://finance.yahoo.com/news/faraday-future-2017-tesla-model-195120592.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年1月4日的[[国际消费电子展|国际消费电子展]]上，法拉第未来展示了他们的单座概念车型，具备{{convert|1000|hp|kW|abbr=on|-1}}以及{{convert|200|mph|km/h|abbr=on|-1}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.faradayfuture.com/ces2016/ |title=Glimpse Into the Future – FFZERO1 Concept |year=2016 |accessdate=2016-01-05 |archive-date=2016-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105070830/http://www.faradayfuture.com/ces2016/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>性能，类似1960年代的[[蝙蝠车|蝙蝠车]]风格。但因没有透露更详细的性能参数，媒体普遍认为它并缺乏量产的可能性<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://electrek.co/2016/01/08/faraday-future-svp-admits-unveiling-the-ffzero1-concept-for-attention-interview-with-nick-sampson-video/|title=Faraday Future SVP admits unveiling the FFZERO1 concept for attention – Interview with Nick Sampson [Video]|last=Lambert|first=Fred|date=2016-01-08|website=Electrek|access-date=2016-12-21|archive-date=2016-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222002017/https://electrek.co/2016/01/08/faraday-future-svp-admits-unveiling-the-ffzero1-concept-for-attention-interview-with-nick-sampson-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年6月17日，法拉第未来在加州获得无人驾驶执照后，开始进行测试<ref name="Buildingselfdriving">{{cite news |url=https://www.yahoo.com/tech/tesla-rival-faraday-approved-test-self-driving-cars-210439778--finance.html |title=Faraday Future to build self-driving vehicles and build and sell electric vehicles |last=Lienert |first=Paul |date=2016-06-21 |work=[[Yahoo_Tech|Yahoo Tech]] |access-date=2016-06-28 |archive-date=2016-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622174913/https://www.yahoo.com/tech/tesla-rival-faraday-approved-test-self-driving-cars-210439778--finance.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Faraday Future Electric Car Company Founders Interview |url=http://dujour.com/lifestyle/faraday-future-founders-electric-cars-interview-pictures/ |website=DuJour |accessdate=2015-12-10 |archive-date=2015-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151217032004/http://dujour.com/lifestyle/faraday-future-founders-electric-cars-interview-pictures/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Mysterious electric car start-up in Gardena has ties to Chinese multibillionaire |url=http://www.latimes.com/business/autos/la-fi-hy-faraday-auto-factory-plan-20151105-story.html |first1=Jerry |last1=Hirsch |first2=Samantha |last2=Masunaga |work=LA Times |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2015-12-10 |archive-date=2015-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151209093100/http://www.latimes.com/business/autos/la-fi-hy-faraday-auto-factory-plan-20151105-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。公司表示将计划探索汽车和技术产业的其他方面，包括驾驶体验、使用模型、车载内容及自动驾驶等<ref>{{Cite news |title=Faraday to reveal its electric car plans at CES in January |url=http://www.reviewjournal.com/news/las-vegas/faraday-reveal-its-electric-car-plans-ces-january |first1=Bethany |last1=Barnes |first2=Sandra |last2=Chereb |work=Las Vegas Review-Journal |date=2015-11-19 |accessdate=2015-12-10 |archive-date=2015-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210214242/http://www.reviewjournal.com/news/las-vegas/faraday-reveal-its-electric-car-plans-ces-january |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=More secrets of EV manufacturer Faraday Future revealed |url=http://www.autoblog.com/2015/12/01/faraday-future-interview/ |work=Autoblog |date=2015-12-01 |accessdate=2015-12-10 |first=Jonathon |last=Ramsey |archive-date=2015-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151213073415/http://www.autoblog.com/2015/12/01/faraday-future-interview/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Meet Dr Bibhrajit Halder of Faraday Future |url=http://auto-sens.com/welcome-to-the-faraday-future/ |work=AutoSens |date=2016-04-04 |accessdate=2015-04-04 |first=Rob |last=Stead |archive-date=2016-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319225145/http://auto-sens.com/welcome-to-the-faraday-future |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年1月的国际消费电子展上，法拉第未来宣布了新型量产汽车FF91<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://electrek.co/2016/12/06/faraday-future-tease-production-electric-ca/|title=Faraday Future teases its first production-intent electric car ahead of unveil next month|last=Lambert|first=Fred|date=2016-12-06|website=Electrek|access-date=2016-12-21|archive-date=2016-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222001653/https://electrek.co/2016/12/06/faraday-future-tease-production-electric-ca/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://electrek.co/2016/10/19/faraday-future-to-unveil-its-first-production-car-at-ces-2017-in-january/ |title=Faraday Future to unveil its first production car at CES 2017 in January |last=Lambert |first=Fred |date=2016-10-19 |website=Electrek |access-date=2016-12-21 |archive-date=2016-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222001619/https://electrek.co/2016/10/19/faraday-future-to-unveil-its-first-production-car-at-ces-2017-in-january/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其{{convert|0-60|mph|km/h|abbr=on|0}}加速度达到2.5秒<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://electrek.co/2016/12/15/faraday-future-electric-crossover-beats-teslas-model-x-p100d-ludicrous/ |title=Faraday Future claims its electric crossover beats Tesla’s Model X P100D Ludicrous in a drag race, releases video |last=Lambert |first=Fred |date=2016-12-15 |website=Electrek |access-date=2016-12-21 |archive-date=2016-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222001912/https://electrek.co/2016/12/15/faraday-future-electric-crossover-beats-teslas-model-x-p100d-ludicrous/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://electrek.co/2016/12/23/faraday-future-prototype-beats-tesla-model-s-p100d/ |title=Faraday Future now claims that its prototype beats the Tesla Model S P100D’s 2.5 seconds 0 to 60 mph |last=Lambert |first=Fred |date=2016-12-23 |website=Electrek |access-date=2016-12-23 |archive-date=2016-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224095139/https://electrek.co/2016/12/23/faraday-future-prototype-beats-tesla-model-s-p100d/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并决定使用可变驱动底盘架构（{{lang|en|Variable Platform Architecture}}）<ref name=VPA>{{cite web|url= http://www.theverge.com/2016/12/22/13908160/faraday-future-vs-ff-cayman-global-problems-jia-leeco-lesee-car |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20161225081101/http://www.theverge.com/2016/12/22/13908160/faraday-future-vs-ff-cayman-global-problems-jia-leeco-lesee-car |title=Behind the scenes at Faraday Future, an electric carmaker on the brink of collapse|date=2016-12-22 |archivedate=2016-12-25 |publisher=Vox Media|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |accessdate= 2016-12-28|deadurl=no}}</ref>。使用在FF91上的纯电动电机峰值功率可以达到783千瓦1050马力，峰值扭矩为1800牛米。售价将会在15万美元至20万美元之间，并将在2018年正式上市销售<ref>{{cite news|title=贾跃亭坎坷造车梦今日见真章 此前屡受资金链困扰|url=http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/t/2017-01-04/doc-ifxzczsu6735102.shtml|accessdate=2017-01-04|agency=证券时报网|date=2017年1月4日|archive-date=2017-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170104170059/http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/t/2017-01-04/doc-ifxzczsu6735102.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=贾跃亭：FF91是最快的电动车 能替代很多车型|url=http://finance.sina.com.cn/chanjing/gsnews/2017-01-04/doc-ifxzizus3629643.shtml|accessdate=2017-01-04|agency=一财网|date=2017年1月4日|archive-date=2017-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170104164044/http://finance.sina.com.cn/chanjing/gsnews/2017-01-04/doc-ifxzizus3629643.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 财务争议 ==
一些法拉第未来前员工、及政府官员曾经对法拉第未来的财政能力表示质疑<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://corp.aol.com/news/nevada-treasurer-raises-questions-about-faraday-future |title=Nevada treasurer raises questions about Faraday Future {{!}} AOL Corporate |website=corp.aol.com |access-date=2016-07-19 |archive-date=2016-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818054051/http://corp.aol.com/news/nevada-treasurer-raises-questions-about-faraday-future |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.autoblog.com/2016/07/10/faraday-future-questions-nevada-treasurer/|title=Nevada treasurer raises questions about Faraday Future|last=King|first=Danny|website=Autoblog|access-date=2016-07-19|archive-date=2016-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715044047/http://www.autoblog.com/2016/07/10/faraday-future-questions-nevada-treasurer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。法拉第未来也未能成立一定规模的信托基金，这导致很多媒体和财务分析师怀疑公司的财务稳定性和总体投资策略<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.wallstreetdaily.com/2016/04/20/faraday-future-electric-cars/ |title=Faraday Future: Is This Car Company Legit? |first=Greg |last=Miller |work=Wall Street Daily |location=US |date=2016-04-20 |access-date=2017-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161209135130/http://www.wallstreetdaily.com/2016/04/20/faraday-future-electric-cars/ |archive-date=2016-12-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

一些分析家认为，法拉第未来的财务资金很大程度依靠主要投资者[[贾跃亭|贾跃亭]]对于上市公司[[乐视网|乐视网]]的股权质押<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-07-04/chinese-billionaire-s-plan-to-trounce-tesla-has-a-vegas-problem|title=The Chinese Billionaire Who Wants to Out-Tesla Tesla|date=2016-07-05|website=Bloomberg|access-date=2016-12-11|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220161453/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-07-04/chinese-billionaire-s-plan-to-trounce-tesla-has-a-vegas-problem|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这导致法两者的财务产生了共振效应<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cleantechnica.com/2016/07/08/faraday-futures-nevada-factory-hits-speed-bump/|title=Faraday Future’s Nevada Factory Hits Speed Bump|website=CleanTechnica|access-date=2016-07-19|archive-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709141455/https://cleantechnica.com/2016/07/08/faraday-futures-nevada-factory-hits-speed-bump/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年11月，法拉第未来在内华达州工厂的进度受到财务限制<ref>{{cite web |url=https://electrek.co/2016/11/15/faraday-future-delays-ev-factory-construction-securing-more-money/ |title=Faraday Future delays EV factory construction while investors secured $600 million in financing |last=Lambert |first=Fred |date=2016-11-15 |work=Electrek |accessdate=2016-11-15 |archive-date=2016-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116021934/https://electrek.co/2016/11/15/faraday-future-delays-ev-factory-construction-securing-more-money/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-leeco-fundraising-idUSKBN13A10K |title=China's Leshi Holdings secures $600 million in support |date=2016-11-15 |work=Reuters |accessdate=2016-11-15 |archive-date=2016-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116021830/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-leeco-fundraising-idUSKBN13A10K |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=hire>{{cite web|url= https://www.buzzfeed.com/priya/turmoil-at-faraday-future |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20161227112048/https://www.buzzfeed.com/priya/turmoil-at-faraday-future |title=Faraday Future Plagued By Lawsuits, Unpaid Bills Ahead Of Electric Car Reveal|date=2016-12-15 |archivedate=2016-12-27 |work=BuzzFeed|accessdate= 2016-12-28 |deadurl=no |quote=Faraday is temporarily adjusting their construction schedule with plans to resume in early 2017,” AECOM said}}
</ref>，并遭到了内华达州官员的批评<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/business/tech/2016-11/22/content_27448085.htm|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229033036/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/business/tech/2016-11/22/content_27448085.htm|title=Outlook bleak for LeEco's Nevada electric vehicle plant|date=2016-11-28|archivedate=2016-12-29|work=China Daily|accessdate=2016-12-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>、以及中国国内媒体的攻击；此事遭到贾跃亭的反驳<ref>{{cite web|url= http://jalopnik.com/nevada-official-claims-that-the-chinese-billionaire-beh-1789426896 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20161227044825/http://jalopnik.com/nevada-official-claims-that-the-chinese-billionaire-beh-1789426896 |title=Nevada Official Claims That The Chinese Billionaire Behind Faraday Future Is Broke|date= 2016-11-28 |archivedate=2016-12-27 |work=Jalopnik |accessdate=2016-12-28 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。
2017年7月10日，公司宣布因財務問題，放棄在內華達州建設工廠的計畫<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/7/10/15948976/faraday-future-halts-factory-nevada-cash-woes|title=Faraday Future abandons plan to build $1 billion electric car factory in Nevada amid cash woes|last=Hawkins|first=Andrew J.|date=2017-07-10|website=The Verge|access-date=2017-07-11|archive-date=2017-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711032546/https://www.theverge.com/2017/7/10/15948976/faraday-future-halts-factory-nevada-cash-woes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年8月，法拉第未来收到来自[[恒大健康|恒大健康]]（[[中國恒大集團|中国恒大集团]]旗下上市公司）的8.54亿美元投资，并出资成立新的合资公司<ref>{{cite web |url=https://cleantechnica.com/2018/08/22/is-faraday-future-back-from-the-dead/ |title=Is Faraday Future Back From The Dead? |first=Steve |last=Hanley |work=Clean Technica |location=US |date=2018-08-22 |access-date=2018-08-24 |archive-date=2018-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823054049/https://cleantechnica.com/2018/08/22/is-faraday-future-back-from-the-dead/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但仅仅两个月后，2018年10月，双方即将对方告到[[香港裁判法院|香港裁判法院]]，贾跃亭谋求终止合同<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://technode.com/2018/10/08/briefing-jia-yuetings-faraday-future-seeks-to-end-deal-with-evergrande-health/ |title=Briefing: Jia Yueting's Faraday Future seeks to end deal with Evergrande Health · TechNode |last=Hu |first=Bailey |date=2018-10-08 |work=TechNode |access-date=2018-10-10 |archive-date=2018-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008095706/https://technode.com/2018/10/08/briefing-jia-yuetings-faraday-future-seeks-to-end-deal-with-evergrande-health/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；同时，法拉第未来开始大规模裁员<ref name="layoffs">{{Cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-faradayfuture-jobs/chinas-ev-maker-faraday-future-plans-lay-offs-20-percent-pay-cuts-idUSKCN1MX0RB |title=China's EV maker Faraday Future plans lay-offs, 20 percent pay cuts |date=2018-10-23 |publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |access-date=2018-10-25 |archive-date=2018-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025070916/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-faradayfuture-jobs/chinas-ev-maker-faraday-future-plans-lay-offs-20-percent-pay-cuts-idUSKCN1MX0RB |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而公司的联合创办人等纷纷离职<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://technode.com/2018/10/31/faraday-future-co-founder-resigns/ |title=Faraday Future co-founder resigns amid company turmoil |last=Udemans |first=Christopher |date=2018-10-31 |work=TechNode |access-date=2018-10-31 |archive-date=2018-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031083539/https://technode.com/2018/10/31/faraday-future-co-founder-resigns/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年3月，[[第九城市|第九城市]]宣布入资6亿美元与法拉第未来成立新的合资公司<ref>{{Cite web|title=贾跃亭获第九城市6亿美元融资|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/tech/2019-03/26/c_1124281327.htm|work=新华网|accessdate=2019-03-26|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327090943/http://www.xinhuanet.com/tech/2019-03/26/c_1124281327.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但市场质疑双方合作能力与经营水平，第九城市股价收跌20%<ref>{{Cite web|title=隔夜美股 三大股指近乎收平 第九城市(NCTY.US)收跌20%|url=https://finance.ifeng.com/c/7lLbJoWYejA|work=凤凰网|accessdate=2019-03-26|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327092459/https://finance.ifeng.com/c/7lLbJoWYejA|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年1月29日，中国[[吉利控股集团|吉利控股集团]]公布與法拉第未來簽署合作協議，吉利與[[鴻海|鴻海]]旗下[[富士康|富士康]]的合資公司有機會為法拉第未來提供代工服務<ref>{{cite news |title=吉利集團或向法拉第未來代工 並參與其上市投資 |url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210129/bkn-20210129095223778-0129_00842_001.html |accessdate=2021-01-30 |work=on.cc東網 |date=2021-01-29 |language=zh-hk |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204124429/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210129/bkn-20210129095223778-0129_00842_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
2021年10月7日，美國沽空機構J Capital Research發表28頁報告，質疑法拉第未來經過8年的經營仍未能交付一輪汽車。<ref>{{cite news |title=賈躍亭旗下FF遭沽空機構狙擊　28頁報告質疑造車能力 |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/686097/%E8%B3%88%E8%BA%8D%E4%BA%AD%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8Bff%E9%81%AD%E6%B2%BD%E7%A9%BA%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A-28%E9%A0%81%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%80%A0%E8%BB%8A%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B |work=[[香港01|香港01]] |date=2021-10-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008050043/https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/686097/%E8%B3%88%E8%BA%8D%E4%BA%AD%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8Bff%E9%81%AD%E6%B2%BD%E7%A9%BA%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A-28%E9%A0%81%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%80%A0%E8%BB%8A%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B |archivedate=2021-10-08}}</ref>

